        <Parent_String>executive records by function [300027795], executive records [300172756], government records by function [300027787], government records [300027777], records by provenance [300027765], records (documents) [300026685], documents by function [300137955], document genres [300026031], information forms (objects) [300220751], Information Forms (hierarchy name) [300026029], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
